OOC:

I'm posting all my characters in one email so here it is:

{Grimlock}

    The dinobot swiftly stomped back to Mximal base the rather beaten and
stomped body of Inferno still clenched in his jaws, the head missing, he
moved up the ramp and into the ship passing by several other maximals to
move towards the brig. Opening a cell he spit the predicons body against the
back wall, "Me Grimlock say you predicons taste funny..." Securing the cell
Grimlock turned away to go back to the mess hall...

{Talos}

    Talos waited calmly for the bot in his office to answer as his comm came
alive with reports. Turning from his guest he opened the comm to Blackfang,
"I have a bot in my office but it seems like the day for guests, what's up?"
he said before opening the comm to Condor, "Talos here Condor, what do you
need, and speak up the comm signal seems to be weak..."

{Nightshade}

    The fem bot turned looking upon Hot Rod as he barged into her new
quarters, a slight smile or smirk crossed her face, "Same old Hot Rod,
impulsive as ever. Been a long time..though I won't hold not recognizing me
against you. This new form is so unlike my hold pink and white vehicle body,
but there wasn't much room for a gal of that size when the down grade
came..." Sighing she sat back on the bunk waving Hot Rod in. "And close the
door, never know when one of those damn Maximals will try taking a pot shot
at me again."
